["class TagVerificationService {","","    func verifyTagsApplied(expectedTags: [String: Any],","                          completion: @escaping (Bool) -> Void) {","","        Pushwoosh.configure.getTags({ tags in","            guard let serverTags = tags else {","                completion(false)","                return","            }","","            let allMatch = expectedTags.allSatisfy { key, expectedValue in","                guard let serverValue = serverTags[key] else { return false }","","                if let expected = expectedValue as? String,","                   let server = serverValue as? String {","                    return expected == server","                }","                if let expected = expectedValue as? NSNumber,","                   let server = serverValue as? NSNumber {","                    return expected == server","                }","                return false","            }","","            completion(allMatch)","","        }, onFailure: { error in","            Logger.error(\"Tag verification failed: \\(error?.localizedDescription ?? \"Unknown\")\")","            completion(false)","        })","    }","}"]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"getTags:onFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"getTags:onFailure:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getTags:onFailure:"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)getTags:onFailure:","roleHeading":"Type Method"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/gettags:onfailure:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfig